01:32:59.940 --> 01:33:03.774
I got you now, Katie.
Oh my God.

01:33:03.811 --> 01:33:05.574
- I'm not gonna let you go.
- Do you love me, Daddy?

01:33:05.612 --> 01:33:08.046
Of course I do. I love you more than
anything in the world.

