What floor?
What floor?

01:40:37.430 --> 01:40:39.557
14th floor, 1408.
Mike Enslin.

01:40:39.599 --> 01:40:42.033
Please come here.

01:40:42.068 --> 01:40:45.868
You're wasting your time.

01:40:51.378 --> 01:40:53.972
We're here
to do the job,

01:40:54.014 --> 01:40:56.141
and we don't rattle.

